  <div class="relative z-10 px-5 sm:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <p class="text-lg !leading-150 text-dark sm:text-2xl">
      Yoredu is your digital ally, your partner in growth, and your gateway to the boundless realm of online learning.
      With an extensive array of courses spanning diverse domains, Yoredu connects you to visionary instructors and
      captivating content. Our sleek interface and cutting-edge features redefine how you experience education, making
      it seamless, enjoyable, and extraordinarily effective.
      <br />
      <br />
